data.label: liboctopus
data.description: 该库提供与 Octopus 格式（及 Octopus Manifest）完全对应的 C++ 数据结构，同时还包含用于简单转换为 JSON 字符串表示的解析器和序列化器。

data.label: liboctopus
data.description: This library provides C++ data structures exactly corresponding to the Octopus format (and Octopus Manifest) and also contains parser and serializer classes for simple conversion to and from a JSON string representation.
